action.description: Passed Second Reading as amended in HD 1; placed on the calendar for Third Reading with Representative(s) Matsumoto, Perruso, Reyes Oda voting aye with reservations; Representative(s) Alcos, Garcia, Muraoka, Shimizu, Souza voting no (5) and Representative(s) Cochran, Pierick, Templo, Ward excused (4).
